meta {
  name: List all client role app targets
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/oauth2/v1/clients/{{clientId}}/roles/{{roleAssignmentId}}/targets/catalog/apps
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Lists all OIN app targets for an `APP_ADMIN` role that's assigned to a client (by `clientId`).

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
